				<tKey>FSFComplexJobsMechanoidsAreCapableTitle</tKey>
			</li>
			<li MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech" Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.SetColor">
				<color>(163,177,188)</color>
			</li>
			<li MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech" Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.Text">
				<text>Changes the canBeDoneByMechs field on all work type tasks from false to true.\nNote: Some tasks break the game without code to further patch the task.  These tasks are not included for obvious reasons.</text>
				<tKey>FSFComplexJobsMechanoidsAreCapableDesc</tKey>
			</li>
			<li MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech" Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.SetColor"/>
			<li MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech" Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.GapLine">
				<spacing>12</spacing>
			</li>
			
